## Privacy

4Charm does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. All downloads are saved locally to your computer. The app only communicates with 4chan's public API to fetch thread data and download media files.

---

**Note**: 4Charm is not affiliated with or endorsed by 4chan. Use responsibly and respect 4chan's terms of service.
